coding.display: Finding related to ability to latch on to breast for feeding

text.div: Patient:
Practitioner: 123

dosageInstruction.text: <prefix>Start</prefix>  <dosage>3 - 3 1/2</dosage>   <formula>cup(s)</formula>    <divider>or</divider> <dosage>720-840</dosage> <unit>ml</unit>     <adjective>every</adjective> <length>4</length> <time>hours</time> <suffix>until urine is clear or there is a normal number of wet diapers</suffix>

<prefix>Start Cotrimoxazole. Give</prefix>  <dosage>3</dosage>   <formula>tablet(s)</formula> <treatment></treatment>   <divider>or</divider> <dosage>1 1/2</dosage>  <measure>teaspoon</measure> <formula>syrup</formula> <treatment></treatment> <length>2</length> <adjective>times a</adjective> <time>day</time> <adjective>for</adjective> <length>5</length> <time>days</time> <suffix>. If Cotrimoxazole not available use treatment for Amoxicillin</suffix>
